      "writtenOn": "2014-12-10T08:31:49Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "You\u0027re right, this should use the SDL2 scancode instead. Unlike SDL1, the keycode is now localized and I missed that difference. I\u0027ll update a fix.\n\nApart from that, I switch between both keyboard pretty frequently. Because SDL 1.x doesn\u0027t support international layout very well, the emulator never tried to be really smart about this. The current code tries to replicate the current behaviour. We should be able to do much better in the future, either with the new frontend, or by improving the SDL2 one once we drop the SDL1 support code.",
      "parentUuid": "c488eee4_b451715c",
      "revId": "6ea6546dc68b018b1d75494222019f815d79d0c6",
